INSERT INTO
            prover_jobs_fri (
                l1_batch_number,
                chain_id,
                circuit_id,
                circuit_blob_url,
                aggregation_round,
                sequence_number,
                depth,
                is_node_final_proof,
                protocol_version,
                status,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                protocol_version_patch
            )
            VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9, 'queued', NOW(), NOW(), $10)
            ON CONFLICT (
                l1_batch_number,
                chain_id,
                aggregation_round,
                circuit_id,
                depth,
                sequence_number
            ) DO
            UPDATE
            SET
            updated_at = NOW()
